Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.60,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  We'll take a fifteen minute break \Nbefore we start the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:10.14,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:14.02,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, I'm heading to the fountain.  \NIf anything comes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:22.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When I play against Kana-chan, \NI can move back seven lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.11,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Same when I play Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.22,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Porky and Taichi are stronger now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.35,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to rush myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll move back three lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.62,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Three-syllable timing...  \NFour-syllable timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.38,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower pe—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:39.84,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So the flower has...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.27,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The storm blasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.98,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}to set the Tatsuta River ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.65,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Timing is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but you also need to have control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:57.07,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How do I get rid of that left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:08.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have besides my speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:29.07,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,If she used 1/10 of that \Nfocus on studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.52,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,her grades wouldn't be fifth \Nfrom the bottom in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:40.74,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:50.14,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}Verse 20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:50.14,Chiha-ep-title-poem-wide,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}The Cresting \NWaves\N Almost\N Look Like \NClouds in \Nthe Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:48.95,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you'll be \Nparticipating in the tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.10,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on Sunday in Kawaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.90,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:56.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why not, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The Yoshino Tournament is the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.41,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,last major tournament before \Nthe Master/Queen qualifiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be participating as-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.57,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,What day is the Monday \Nfollowing the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:06.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Marine Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.23,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The first day of exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.83,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you're \Ngoing to be held back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Seriously?  For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:18.76,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that you are \Ndedicated to karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:23.47,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,but you need to start \Nthinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:24.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My future...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.39,queen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.55,East qual,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}East Qualifier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.39,shinobu,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shinobu-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.97,Yoshino,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Yoshino Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.97,recently,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,What's recently been on her mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.97,food,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Food
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.97,black,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}The new \NDaddy Bear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.97,future,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.97,first,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,First\N appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.48,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,So I found a tutor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.86,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,He'll go over every one of your courses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.86,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with you in the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.80,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.45,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Tutor".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.86,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.03,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.81,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the verge of failing \NEnglish and Math...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.37,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Yoshino \NTournament tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.58,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino only has brackets \Nfor Class A and Class B,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.00,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,If we aren't going to practice today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.76,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head over to the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.68,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.63,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You placed second at Nationals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.91,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Saitama tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.64,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you're allowed to advance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.13,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to Class A if you've \Nplaced second twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.71,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Have you asked the \NShiranami Society coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:17.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He said that I had to \Nwin a tournament first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.84,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You too?  That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.40,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Our society's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.38,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So when I told everyone I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.14,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome, Yusei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.91,Chiha-flashback,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to Coach and the \Nother players at this society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:32.91,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.47,Chiha-flashback,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me mad, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.35,Chiha-flashback,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are the reason the old you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.86,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,who hates to lose, is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.47,Chiha-flashback,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.15,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I can only advance if I win, \Nso that's what I'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.78,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.80,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants to play in this \Nyear's Eastern qualifier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.95,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants to make Class A this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is his last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.76,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to try to learn anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.69,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,So memorize!  Memorize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.32,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Treat this like a match \Nand memorize hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.14,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll forget it \Nall before the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:23.09,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I made it past the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.51,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a roll today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.26,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.43,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the next round,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.66,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,my matches will be in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.74,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Class A matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.87,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.66,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,You're winning games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.42,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Dr. Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.77,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm winning, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.47,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing the best karuta I can, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.21,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Class A players all participate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.28,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Yoshino Tournament to \Nprepare for the Master Qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.48,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,There are players from \NKansai and Kyushu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.04,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,It's an excellent chance to see how \Nyou match up against the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.11,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's preparing for \Nthe Master qualifiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.66,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.05,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.  \NHave you run into him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.21,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:15.68,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.76,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hasn't Ayase been in the restroom a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.97,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Number two.  \NThat or she fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.20,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot to put my phone on vibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.71,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tutor.\NI'm going to cheer for Taichi. \N-Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:40.10,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.40,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.05,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.05,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Harada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:56.29,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ages since the last \Ntime you came to Kanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.16,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,My knees have been killing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.45,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I had to come along
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:03.25,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,since so many of our \Nplayers are participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.81,Chiha-overlap,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kuriyama and Dr. Harada
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.84,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get those knees patched up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.57,Chiha-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,have been rivals since they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.41,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can play karuta again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.84,Chiha-overlap,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kuriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.80,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.57,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,We need to watch our health.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.06,Chiha-overlap,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,He's the director of the Nagumo Society, \Nwhere I'm registered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.53,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.07,Chiha-main,Harada,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.28,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The third round for Class A \Nand Class B will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.36,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please move to your assigned seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.49,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.88,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.18,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.18,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would be in the \NClass A tournament today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.23,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Pass that on to Chihaya,\N if she needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.94,handwriting,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.07,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.53,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata... is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.91,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:05.67,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.23,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:12.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:13.96,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.68,cellphone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.68,cellphone3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that you're running \Naway from your responsibilities.\N-From your tutor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's so calm when he's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.22,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.66,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting nowhere with \Nstudying or karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:46.65,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, what if Taichi is all \Nalone when he wins or loses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.35,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Well?  Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.67,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What round is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.28,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.54,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata is playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:29.98,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,for there is no one else out here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:49.08,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,As I wait for someone \Nwho will never come,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.65,Chiha-note,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:10:02.99,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,my body burns like the seaweed \Ndrying on the shores of Matsuho
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.66,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.09,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.21,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.34,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I won my game by 11 cards to \Nmake it to the semifinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.51,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.27,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.96,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When I must hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.66,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Would the mountain cherry blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.06,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When the misty bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.56,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When winds send waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.44,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.62,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Arata's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.53,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.54,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.42,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.07,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It happened, Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.20,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.75,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's going to come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.31,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,so we have to become stronger \Nand wait for his return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:18.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.72,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me didn't want to see him here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.54,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but deep down, I'm celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:33.88,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.00,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.49,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.  Really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.28,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboguchi Hiroshi-san,\N from the Shiranami Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.61,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,One more card! \N One more card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.05,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Give me "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:58.51,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,"For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.89,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.38,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,"For the"!  "For the"!  "For the"!  "For the"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.63,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense Dr. Harada behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:15.83,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,leaving a hovering mist \Nabove the trees and grass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.23,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,For the cold nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.81,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.75,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.31,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I got the card?  Terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:35.00,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,But that was pure luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.81,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I chose a card and moved before \NI heard the first syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.17,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he still almost got there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.68,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I would have lost if either of the \Nother two cards had been read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.22,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The semifinals will \Nbegin in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.92,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san is our ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.28,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going to lose to someone who \Nhasn't played in eighteen months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.01,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you need to-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.86,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he go for that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How does he stay still when \Na dead card is read?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.64,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What is his thinking process \Nfor sending cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?  How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:25.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.70,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.58,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.41,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.61,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even playing,\N and you're already fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:11.97,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.03,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.83,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Huh?  \NYou came, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.36,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We all wanted to cheer \Nfor the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.39,disguise,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,A disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.35,Chiha-overlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!  I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:22.15,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,yet Desktomu-kun agreed \Nto help you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.35,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.82,Chiha-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,go grab your fourth place award.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.64,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Then you ran off by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.57,Chiha-overlap,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.55,Chiha-main,Arata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.61,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.32,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody from the Nagumo Society is left,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.16,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and we drove here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.78,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.42,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be the middle of the \Nnight when we reach Fukui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can give this to her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.17,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Your cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:46.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me decide \Nif she needs it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.63,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.29,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Right away?!  Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.95,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:56.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.43,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.43,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't know if the two \Nof you were a couple now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No, definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.91,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.99,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually pretty \Nsensitive about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.56,Chiha-flashbackinternal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.77,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.40,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You can't afford to \Nwaste a single second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.25,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Read your textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.89,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not on the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.26,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Start from page 92 for Classic Lit.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.01,genji,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The Tale of Genji\NLady Murasaki Shikibu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.20,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.40,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Lady Murasaki Shikibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to fit Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I get to meet him, \Nhe has to leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a love poem,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.29,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But this poem is about a girl who\Nwas her childhood friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:08.79,card1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Lady Murasaki Shikibu\N\NLong last we meet,\N only for me to leave hurriedly,\Nfor I could not recognize you, \Nlike the moon hidden behind the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.79,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a love poem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.18,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,No swinging on the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.33,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It was like water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,flowing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:29.37,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was gulping down soft water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.00,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about running off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:52.52,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan sent a message to \Nlet us know how Mashima did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.  \NHe lost in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.97,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Was he depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.81,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima spends most of \Nhis time on karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.98,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but he always has the top \Ntest scores in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.77,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't, he'll have \Nto quit the karuta club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.40,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do the things \Nyou don't want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.41,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,before you can do the things \Nyou truly want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.08,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry! \N I'm going to study hard now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.63,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I've mastered English already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.71,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:32.77,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, we close at 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.72,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lock up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.39,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyauchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.07,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.88,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that I also lost,\N but how could you lose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.15,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,by 11 cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.95,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I felt so content after \Nmy match with Wataya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.72,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.55,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.20,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How was your match against Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:10.65,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I hated it. \N Really hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.91,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,He was clearly thinking \Nthrough every move,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.46,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.97,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.73,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Master Suo wouldn't bat \Nan eye against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.58,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:26.17,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He mentioned the Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.09,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,while talking about a player in his
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.00,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,first year of high school who just made Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.89,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.67,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.27,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san is looking ahead \Nto the Master qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:42.28,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I should have watched them play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.18,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I should have watched from \Nthe very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.90,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.21,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.15,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:20:00.42,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You placed second in two Class B \Ntournaments this summer, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.25,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,If we go by the official standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.93,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're qualified to be in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.93,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,This would break the \NShiranami Society rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.69,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but would you like me to promote you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.78,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to Class A so you can \Nplay in the East qualifier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:20.52,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan and Glasses are \Nwaiting for you in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.43,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Promote?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.65,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,An empty train is passing \Nthrough platform 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.29,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Frustration will not last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.52,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can keep on going \Nwithout some measure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.88,Chiha-internal,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,of reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.71,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do that, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:45.68,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:50.56,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, I'm not so much \Nfocused on making Class A
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.81,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,as I'm focused on becoming \Nsomeone who doesn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.61,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.62,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,He was nervous about \Nmeeting his old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.63,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it was worth the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.58,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.97,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp it all down.
